src:
Gempa M 5,3 Terjadi di Melonguane, Sulut
01 Nov 2019, 09:51 by Danu Damarjati
Jakarta - Gempa magnitudo (M) 5,3 mengguncang sebelah tenggara Melonguane, Sulawesi Utara. Gempa ini tidak berpotensi tsunami.
Diinformasikan oleh Badan Meteorologi Klimatologi dan Geofisika (BMKG), gempa terjadi pada Jumat (1/11/2019) pukul 09.33 WIB.
Gempa ini berpusat di 93 km sebelah tenggara Melonguane, tepatnya di koordinat 3,25 Lintang Utara dan 127,07 Bujur Timur.
"Tidak berpotensi tsunami," kata BMKG.

(dnu/jbr)
text:
5.3 M earthquake occurred in Melonguane, North Sulawesi
Nov 01 2019, 09:51 by Danu Damarjati
Jakarta - A magnitude 5.3 (M) earthquake shook southeast of Melonguane, North Sulawesi. This earthquake did not trigger a tsunami.
Informed by the Climatology and Geophysics Meteorology Agency (BMKG), the earthquake occurred on Friday (11/01/2019) at 09.33 WIB.
This earthquake was centered at 93 km southeast of Melonguane, precisely at the coordinates of 3.25 North Latitude and 127.07 East Longitude.
"There is no potential for a tsunami," BMKG said.

(dnu / jbr)
